                    "value": 1
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p><strong>Frequency</strong> once per day</p><hr /><p><strong>Effect</strong> Nayren's strikes keeps them empowered to continue to take down rebels. For 1 minute or until they critically miss, the first time each round Nayren successfully Strikes a creature, they gain 5 temporary Hit Points that last for 1 round.</p>"
